Remove example test files, clean up arrow syntax

Removed sum.js and sum.test.js example test files for Jest.
Refactored anonymous functions to use arrow function notation.

Clean up more code

Went through and cleaned up some more code so that it has consistent style.

Clean up strings to use single quotes and interpolation.

The strings were being represented with both single and double quotes, so I standardized them to use
single quotes. I also replaced string concatenation with ES6-style interpolation.
